<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Day Vy Cosmetics</title>
</head>
    <style type="text/css">
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            height: 100vh;
            min-width: 100%;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #222222;
        
        }

        a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration:none;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.25;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .status {
            color: #fff;
            width: 100px;
            padding: 10px;
            animation: blink 2s infinite;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        @keyframes blink {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
            }

            to {
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }

        p {
            margin: 0;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .divider {
            border-top: 1px solid #ccc;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .email-wrapper {
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .email-header {
            background-color: #1e1e1e;
            padding: 30px;
            color: #f086d9;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .email-body {
            padding: 14px;
            background-color: #f4f3f3;
            height: 70vh;
        }

        .email-footer {
            background-color: #1e1e1e;
            padding: 14px;
            color: #d55fbb;
            text-align: center;
        }

        img {
            padding: 24px;
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }
        .highlight-excited {
            color: #d63384;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
    </style>
    <body 
        <div class="email-wrapper">
            <div class="email-header">
                <img src="https://i.ibb.co/3p0m0ZV/logo.png" alt="Day Vy Cosmetics Logo">
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <h1>Welcome to Day-Vy Cosmetics!</h1>
            <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
            <p>Thank you for joining us. We are <span class="highlight-excited">excited</span> to have you as part of our community.</p>
            <p>We're here to help you discover products that match your style and elevate your beauty routine.</p>
            <p>Enjoy shopping with exclusive offer, beauty tip and discover your favourite products</p>
            <p>If you have any questions or need further assistance, feel free to <a href="mailto:support@day-vy-cosmetics.com" style="color:#d63384;font-weight:bold;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;">support@day-vy-cosmetics.com</a>.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>&copy;2025 Day-Vy Cosmetics. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
	</body>
</html>
